# API Endpoints

This document describes the main API endpoints of the Retail Order Automation System.

## Upload Page

GET /ui/upload

Displays the page where the user can upload Excel files for order generation.

---

## Generate Order

POST /generate-order/

Accepts five Excel files:

- current_stock.xlsx
- sales.xlsx
- onway_stock.xlsx
- MinQ.xlsx
- Calendar.xlsx

The system processes the data and calculates the optimal order quantities.

The result is returned as a downloadable Excel file.

---

## Order History

GET /ui/history

Displays the list of previously generated orders stored in the database.

---

## Dashboard

GET /ui/dashboard

Displays analytics information such as:

- Top suppliers
- Top products
- Average order quantity             